<paragraph id="628BE62A5E712AE0062E42A88CC1D0C3" pageId="18" pageNumber="67">
Treatment of the genus by 
<bibRefCitation id="570B7C836745E4D6D494DDA4598B3F66" author="Gilbert, MG" journalOrPublisher="Kew Bulletin" pageId="50" pageNumber="99" pagination="165 - 193" publicationUrl="10.2307/4113733" refId="B11" refString="Gilbert, MG, Jeffrey, C, 1988. A revision of Ethulia (Compositae: Vernonieae). Kew Bulletin 43 (2): 165 - 193, DOI: 10.2307/4113733" title="A revision of Ethulia (Compositae: Vernonieae)." url="10.2307/4113733" volume="43" year="1988">Gilbert and Jeffrey (1988)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
